OL,3,CVisa change destroying notion of UK as
OL,4,Cplace for families, say campaigners
OL,6,FChanges to visa rules costing people
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds extra "destroy the
OL,8,Fnotion of the UK as a place where
OL,9,Ffamilies can thrive", campaigners said
OL,10,Fas a new mother told of struggling
OL,11,Fwith separation from her husband.
OL,13,FAs the minimum income for family visas
OL,14,Frose by more than #10,000 to #29,000
OL,15,Ffrom Thursday, the organisation
OL,16,FReunite Families UK claimed the values
OL,17,Fof family and love are being treated
OL,18,Fas "as yet another political football
OL,19,Fto be sacrificed in order to receive
OL,20,Fbetter poll or electoral results".
