OL,3,CVisa change destroying notion of UK as
OL,4,Cplace for families, say campaigners
OL,6,FThe measures, first announced in
OL,7,FDecember, are part of what the
OL,8,FGovernment has described as "an
OL,9,Faccelerated and comprehensive
OL,10,Fprogramme of reforms" to address
OL,11,F"unsustainable" levels of legal
OL,12,Fmigration to the UK.
OL,14,FThe minimum income requirement will
OL,15,Frise further to #38,700 by early 2025.
