OL,3,CVisa change destroying notion of UK as
OL,4,Cplace for families, say campaigners
OL,6,FIt had remained unchanged for more
OL,7,Fthan a decade, and helps to ensure
OL,8,Ffamilies are self-sufficient and not
OL,9,Frelying on public funds, whilst making
OL,10,Fa positive impact on the economy, the
OL,11,FHome Office said.
OL,13,FBut Argentinian Eugenia Morales said
OL,14,Fthe uncertainty around her and her
OL,15,Fseven month-old baby daughter being
OL,16,Fable to reunite with her husband in
OL,17,Fthe UK has taken a toll on her mental
OL,18,Fhealth.
