OL,3,CVisa change destroying notion of UK as
OL,4,Cplace for families, say campaigners
OL,6,FThe 30-year-old has been with her
OL,7,Fpartner Connor White for three years
OL,8,Fbut is unsure now whether, after
OL,9,Fhaving their daughter in her home
OL,10,Fcountry, she will be able to join him
OL,11,Fin England.
OL,13,FShe said Mr White, who is based in
OL,14,FWest Sussex, cannot leave his eldest
OL,15,Fchild from a previous relationship and
OL,16,Fhas been working weekends in his
OL,17,Fconstruction job to try and boost his
OL,18,Fincome to the required amount to
OL,19,Fsponsor his wife.
