OL,3,CVisa change destroying notion of UK as
OL,4,Cplace for families, say campaigners
OL,6,FMs Morales said she would be looking
OL,7,Ffor a job in the UK and would not have
OL,8,Faccess to benefits while applying on
OL,9,Fthe family visa route anyway.
OL,11,FShe told the PA news agency: "We don't
OL,12,Fwant to be a burden to the (welfare)
OL,13,Fsystem, we just want to be with our
OL,14,Ffamilies."
OL,16,FDescribing the situation as "very
OL,17,Fhard", she said: "It's an awful
OL,18,Fsituation. We want to be together, we
OL,19,Fwant the girls to grow up together but
OL,20,Fthis is making it totally impossible."
