OL,3,CVisa change destroying notion of UK as
OL,4,Cplace for families, say campaigners
OL,6,FColin Whitley from Halifax, West
OL,7,FYorkshire, said he has been working
OL,8,Fsix-day weeks to try to have enough
OL,9,Fmoney to sponsor his partner to join
OL,10,Fhim in the UK from Iran.
OL,12,FThe bus driver, 43, said the past few
OL,13,Fmonths have been "really stressful".
OL,15,FHe told PA: "Why should I, as a
OL,16,FBritish citizen, be forced to leave
OL,17,Fthe country which is my home to be
OL,18,Ftogether with the person I have fallen
OL,19,Fin love with? You cannot help who you
OL,20,Ffall in love with."
