OL,3,CVisa change destroying notion of UK as
OL,4,Cplace for families, say campaigners
OL,6,FHe said the Government is "twisting in
OL,7,Fsuch a way to make people think that
OL,8,Fbecause we want to bring our partners
OL,9,Fhere, they're a burden to the
OL,10,Ftaxpayer. But they're not."
OL,12,FHe said his partner, who cannot live
OL,13,Fopenly as a gay man in Iran due to the
OL,14,Flaws there, would work in the UK and
OL,15,Fcontribute to the economy if he had
OL,16,Fthe chance to move.
