OL,6,FA Home Office blog addressing the
OL,7,Fquestion of whether the new rules
OL,8,Fcould risk splitting up families notes
OL,9,Fa provision in immigration rules for
OL,10,Fexceptional circumstances if a refusal
OL,11,Fof a visa application is deemed to
OL,12,Fhave unjustifiably harsh consequences.
OL,14,FBut Caroline Coombs, co-founder of
OL,15,FReunite Families UK, said people are
OL,16,Ffeeling "punished" and "excluded" by
OL,17,Fthe new rules, with what counts as
OL,18,Fexceptional needing to meet "a very
OL,19,Fhigh bar".
