OL,3,CVisa change destroying notion of UK as
OL,4,Cplace for families, say campaigners
OL,6,FMs Coombs said: "This increase,
OL,7,Ftogether with the ones which will come
OL,8,Finto force in the next 12 months
OL,9,Fdestroy the notion of the UK as a
OL,10,Fplace where families can thrive.
OL,12,F"We are dealing with a community of
OL,13,Fmembers who are punished and feel
OL,14,Fexcluded and discriminated by their
OL,15,Fown government only because they fell
OL,16,Fin love with somebody from abroad and
OL,17,Fdo not or cannot (for a variety of
OL,18,Freasons including caring for children
OL,19,Fand/or elderly parents) earn the
OL,20,F'right amount' to be able to love
OL,21,Fwhoever they choose.
