OL,4,Cplace for families, say campaigners
OL,6,FMeanwhile the Migration Observatory at
OL,7,Fthe University of Oxford has done
OL,8,Fanalysis suggesting that between
OL,9,Fentering the UK on a temporary visa
OL,10,Fand becoming a British citizen, most
OL,11,Fmigrants will pay cumulative fees of
OL,12,Fbetween #5,000 and #37,000, depending
OL,13,Fon the visa type and whether they have
OL,14,Fdependants.
OL,16,FThis equates to an annual #2 billion
OL,17,Fincome stream for the Home Office, it
OL,18,Fsaid.
