OL,6,FHome Secretary James Cleverly said
OL,7,F"mass migration" had reached a
OL,8,F"tipping point", adding: "There is no
OL,9,Fsimple solution or easy decision which
OL,10,Fcuts numbers to levels acceptable to
OL,11,Fthe British people."
OL,13,FHe said he had "promised action and we
OL,14,Fhave delivered at remarkable speed".
