OL,4,Cplace for families, say campaigners
OL,6,FHe said: "We've acted to cut
OL,7,Funsustainable numbers, to protect
OL,8,FBritish workers and their wages, to
OL,9,Fensure those bringing family to the UK
OL,10,Fdo not burden taxpayers, and to build
OL,11,Fan immigration system fit for the
OL,12,Ffuture ` and one the public can
OL,13,Frightly have confidence in."
OL,15,FThe Government said the minimum income
OL,16,Frequirement can also be met through
OL,17,Fsavings or, if the applicant is in the
OL,18,FUK already on a different visa,
OL,19,Fthrough their additional income.
